asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

I mean, which stylish horses, I mean Zebras, out there dont want to shimmy or whinny up there appearance with some bling bling to attract the special laaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaydy (cough, clears throat). description: Raised as a professional fighter from a young fluflet, I was winning ti tles for as long as I can remember. Then I feel victim to my addiction to Fluf Nip, that strange plant that on its own has health benefits, but when you concentrate it, it ends up making you be able to stay awake 24 hours 7 days. After battling this addiction for a number of years, losing friends, family, isolating myself, and not realising I had a problem. Ultimately I hit rock bottom, tried Real Deathing myself a number of times, but never managed to destroy my cortical stack. After meeting a number of incredible Fluf such as Crystal Eyes and Cerebro, I chose a path of love, helped let go of my past stories, and embraced mycelium and carrots. Now I am back better than ever in the Fluf Vegas fighting scene, entertaining all of the metaverse with my fancy hop work and padded paws. Im glad we always get a second chance, in fact, without the rock bottom, I would not have appreciated where I am at now. See you ringside FLUFS!
